# ── .NET build output ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
bin/
obj/
*.user
*.suo
.vs/
*.ncrunch*
TestResults/

# ── JetBrains Rider / ReSharper ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
*.DotSettings
*.DotSettings.user
*.rsuser

# ── VS Code ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/

# ── Frontend build output (Vite → wwwroot) ───────────────────────────────────
# Generated by `npm run build` — never commit. Run Publish-PassReset.ps1 instead.
src/PassReset.Web/wwwroot/
src/PassReset.Web/ClientApp/dist/
src/PassReset.Web/ClientApp/.vite/

# ── Node ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/

# ── Deploy publish output and release zips ───────────────────────────────────
# Zips are distributed exclusively via GitHub Releases — never commit binaries.
deploy/publish/
deploy/*.zip
deploy/_staging/

# ── Secrets — never commit ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
appsettings.Production.json
appsettings.*.local.json
secrets.json
*.pfx
*.p12

# ── Personal scratch files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
Todo.MD

# ── Local tooling / IDE metadata ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/
.bg-shell/
.gsd/

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/

# ── OS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*.tmp
*.temp
